{"tid":1823204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有班大專生整左條反送中微電影","createTime":"2020-01-13T13:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:50:30.000Z","uid":148317,"like":58,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"49f709a394df0bf3511b20e755643d75c6fd7d00","tid":1823204,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇睇下youtube見到有條片，係光復香港，時代革命嘅微電影&lt;&lt;習慣&gt;&gt;。 雖然成條片有d位聲同剪接都有待改善。但開頭個部分做引入整得好好，現實就好似大白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中間個幕個男仔扮便衣曱甴捉手足幾逼真，但唔夠真曱甴仆街。最後出現2019年成個畫面同文宣，真係喊出黎，回憶通通出曬嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然條片有d不足，但見到條片嘅簡介，原來係一班大專生去做group project整作出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到有大專生唔怕被學校打壓去交一份有政治立場嘅功課。值得一讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係睇翻個view數只係得40個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手足一齊入去睇爆佢。入去比Like，推爆佢。 一班學生為左鼓勵大家繼續行，比更多人知香港人抗爭，唔知佢哋有冇試過比學校打壓。都選擇去拍關於抗爭片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><strong><strong><strong>最後我睇到好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望手足一齊推爆，Like爆條片，報答翻班學生。</strong></strong></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\nsorry我講到1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有記住1月19大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ByfA4gE_PP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FByfA4gE_PP4&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHHKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=905729b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ByfA4gE_PP4</a><br />\n<br />\n支持黃色影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93a2fe1561b1e450a8a1a7e80dcdf79545dbb5b","tid":1823204,"uid":148317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747d5024db95c05c7fb50283b41e6ac8680a6eba","tid":1823204,"uid":49275,"like":